OsiSolverInterface for AMPL .nl file input

Extends OsiTMINLPInterface to read problems from AMPL .nl files.
Provides convenient entry point for AMPL-based modeling.

**Usage:**
@code
AmplInterface solver;
solver.readAmplNlFile(argv, roptions, options, journalist);
@endcode

**Additional features:**
- readNames(): Read variable/row names from .col/.row files
- amplModel(): Access underlying AmplTMINLP
